De Lima, North Korea, Pacquiao | Evening wRap Watch the evening newscast with Ana Arceo Published 8:31 PM, February 13, 2017 Updated 6:56 PM, February 14, 2017 
Today on Rappler: 
Senator Leila de Lima says she's " ready for arrest ." Justice Secretary Vitaliano Aguirre goes after BuCor legal chief who wrote controversial memo. President Rodrigo Duterte says " nothing I can do over mining closures ." North Korea missile test successful . Manny Pacquiao asks Twitter followers to pick next opponent . Production Staff
